subject: packaging: disable -mfpu=neon for arm builds in all profiles
commitMessage:
packaging: disable -mfpu=neon for arm builds in all profiles

Disable neon by default for all profiles so that the package will build
for newly added profiles, like Tizen:TV. It seems that neon is disabled
in qtbase for every profile anyway - either through OBS prjconf or
through the spec file.

Change-Id: I8ac10d6596b2727895c0d97da1e13994e1220d14
